weo_ultimate = read_excel("WEO_Data_All.xlsx")
weo_ultimate
## # A tibble: 80  3
##    Year  Publication_Date Value

##  1 2010  April_2010        1.28
##  2 2010  April_2011        3.23

##  6 2010  April_2018        1.63

##  9 2011  October_2014      4.88
## 10 2011  October_2015      4.88
## #  70 more rows
ggplot(weo_ultimate, aes(x = Year, y = Value, color = Publication_Date, group = Publication_Date)) +
  geom_line() +
  geom_point() +
  ggtitle("UAE % Actual GDP Change", subtitle = "2010-2028") +
  ylab("Percentage") +
  theme(axis.text.x = element_text(angle = 90, vjust = 0.5, hjust = 1))

weo_actual = read_excel("WEO_Data_actual_datafied.xlsx")
weo_actual
## # A tibble: 45  3
##     Year Publication_Date Value
##    <dbl> <chr>            <dbl>
##  1  2010 April_2010        1.28
##  2  2010 April_2011        3.23
##  3  2010 October_2014      1.64
##  4  2010 October_2015      1.64
##  5  2010 April_2017        1.64
##  6  2010 April_2018        1.63
##  7  2010 October_2023      5.28
##  8  2011 April_2011        3.3 
##  9  2011 October_2014      4.88
## 10  2011 October_2015      4.88
## #  35 more rows
ggplot(weo_actual, aes(x = Year, y = Value, color = Publication_Date, group = Publication_Date)) +
  geom_line() +
  geom_point() +
  ggtitle("UAE % Actual GDP Change", subtitle = "2010-2023") +
  ylab("Percentage") +
  scale_x_continuous(breaks = weo_actual$Year, labels = weo_actual$Year) +
  theme(axis.text.x = element_text(angle = 90, vjust = 0.5, hjust = 1)) 

weo_oct = read_excel("October_Actual_Projections.xlsx")
weo_oct
## # A tibble: 14  2
##    time_frame October_2023
##         <dbl>        <dbl>
##  1       2010        5.28 
##  2       2011        6.22 
##  3       2012        1.82 
##  4       2013        5.06 
##  5       2014        4.17 
##  6       2015        6.79 
##  7       2016        5.56 
##  8       2017        0.735
##  9       2018        1.31 
## 10       2019        1.11 
## 11       2020       -4.96 
## 12       2021        4.36 
## 13       2022        7.85 
## 14       2023        3.38
ggplot(weo_oct, aes(x = time_frame, y = October_2023, color = time_frame)) +
  geom_line() +
  geom_point() +
  ggtitle("UAE % Actual GDP Change", subtitle = "2010-2023") +
  scale_x_continuous(breaks = weo_oct$time_frame, labels = weo_oct$time_frame) +
  xlab("Year") +
  ylab("Percentage") +
  theme(axis.text.x = element_text(angle = 90, vjust = 0.5, hjust = 1), legend.position = "none")
